it.ly/30DSNv1</a><br />\n】<br />\n【🎒撐學生計劃：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2D810zV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2D810zV&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=30ad6d03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2D810zV</a><br />\n】<br />\n【🎁贈閱券計劃：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2EPGJj1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EPGJj1&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=ae76c930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2EPGJj1</a><br />\n】<br />\n<br />\n支持《壹週刊》<br />\n【📒訂閱《壹週刊》：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PH5Arq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PH5Arq&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=ce14aa1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2PH5Arq</a><br />\n】<br />\n【💪和你撐計劃：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3aeq4Bq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aeq4Bq&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=9c69b287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3aeq4Bq</a><br />\n 】<br />\n【👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦 贈閱券計劃：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3gKdb4v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3gKdb4v&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=0df22488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3gKdb4v</a><br />\n】<br />\n=====================<br />\n8月10日 #港版國安法 新聞：<br />\n【壹傳媒聲明】堅守崗位，撐到底！<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2FaJYld\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FaJYld&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=763b8503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2FaJYld</a><br />\n<br />\n【警搜《蘋果》全紀錄：歷史在看】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2DSnpks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2DSnpks&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=55e2f1a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2DSnpks</a><br />\n<br />\n【壹工會：歷史會記下這一天發生的事】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31FQFDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=h